texts.text: >You arrive at the shrine on the summit after handling the demons.
I am Taisei, son of Jogan and head of the Yamamoto Clan!
I have come to offer this enchanted sword as part of the "Haja Blade Ritual"!
>Something emerges from the shrine as Taisei finishes speaking.
Ah, Jogan's heir. You have done well to finally reach me,
I am the sword deity, Futsunushi.
This final trial will determine if your sword will become the Haja Blade.
Answer me this. What is a sword to you?
A blade that cuts down even the most ferocious enemies.
Very well. You must prove your resolve to me during this trial.
This mist... I can't see! Everyone, where did you go?!
Ah, so I must do this alone. No help will come then, I see.

*Chuckle*
Can you face my blade?
>Taisei is surrounded by countless demons.
You wish to see if I can defeat all of you with this sword?
This many... I understand why this is the final trial!

*Snicker*
I am still here. Will you not face my blade?

*Pant*
There's just too many...
Himika, good work with your barrier.
Yes, of course. Thank you for aiding me, Seiran.
I... I feel worse though...
This is bad. The energy's growing thicker...
Huh? The barrier's been broken...!
Bad news! Demons are appearing all over Shinjuku!
People are going berserk too! It must be because of these demons!
Shiang Sun?! Do you read me?!
Y-Yes. I'm fine...
Seiran, Himika... Can you cast another barrier?
I believe I can hold the line until then!
Copy. We're on it!
>Seiran and Himika open the doors to the Hideout...
The Demon Users are here? They mustn't get in the way!
They're already here...?!
Move it! Devil Download!
*Shriek*
Get to Shiang Sun while you can!
These things probably sniffed us out somehow.
A second wave is probably right behind them too.
We gotta gather everyone from this branch back here. Time to play some defense.
R-Right...
(I thought we had the edge, but this is too many...)
(Everyone's doing what they can to fight this energy...)
(But we're getting to a point of no return...)
(If Megakin and the others don't succeed with that ritual then...)
(Tokyo will be helpless and completely consumed.)
(The fate of Tokyo lies in the hands of Taisei, Megakin and...)
I'm being told that Tokyo is in danger of being destroyed at any moment...
Priskorbnyy. We cannot deny that possibility.
That's fine. Even if Tokyo is destroyed, the Summoning Room will be safe.
Arisa... This might not be the best time for jokes like that.
Man, you really do have a few screws loose...
But Himika is placing another barrier around here,
and we may be safe as long as you're here with us, Vince.
Let me be clear, I'm here to guard Honey, not the rest of you.
Yes, we understand. Let us know if we can help as well.
>Taisei's battle against the demons begins to take it's toll...
If I don't defeat them all, Tokyo will be destroyed...
But I cannot do this alone...!
Maybe I wasn't ready for this, as father said...

*Pant*
If I don't regroup, I'll... Huh?
SHIONYAN! I knew I was moving in the right direction!
Ugh! Why is it always you?! Anyways, we need to find the others.
Yes, ma'am! Engaging sensors... Hey, over there!

*Pant*
Meat Balloon? Finally, found ya...
Wait! This one looks like... Jeng Yun!
Everyone! I'm glad you're all safe!
What the hell is this "sensor" you're talking about?!
Anything for you, Shionyan!
Well, uh... I guess, good job...
Huh! This one's...
*Hiss*

*Pant*
Another one! Devil Download!

*Pant*
Yo, it's just endless...
Damn... Retreating might be our best option at this point.
I agree. We won't be able to see until Taisei finishes his trial.
And we don't have the strength to hold out until then.
I understand how you feel, Gakuto and Shiori...
But if we let Taisei die here, Tokyo will be doomed.
Only an enchanted sword made by the Yamamoto Clan can suppress this evil...
Leave it to me. I will make sure he succeeds even if it kills me.
Any guarantees?
None. Please, you must trust me.
Yo, but the fate of Tokyo is in Taisei's hands...
Let's believe.
We have to do this.
Thank you.
Yes, this is the only way.
Aight. Kangaroo Boxer, we're in your hands.
Except that "if it kills me" bit. Yo, we're gettin' outta here alive.
Of course. I promise...
>Jeng Yun and the Liberators venture deeper into the mist...
(This blinding mist. Taisei must be in the same situation.)
>Taisei falls to a knee while being surrounded by demons...

*Strike*
Ha! Yah!
*Scream*
Taisei! Are you okay?!
(I'm out of demons. I have to fight them directly now.)
*Roar*
>Jeng Yun relentlessly attacks the demons, but as he does...
What a monstrous demon... Such power... It must be the source!
>Taisei attacks Jeng Yun.
Once I've dealt with you, this trial will be over! Hah!
Taisei?! It's me, Jeng Yun!
Making such unwholesome noises... I will silence you!
Taisei! Please, wake up!
What the hell's going on?! Did he lose it?!
>Now, everything looks like a demon to Taisei.
>Futsunushi observes while wearing a grim expression.
